"Forgive Me" will be Leona Lewis' third single in uk, after her hits "Bleeding Love" & "Better In Time", a new song produced by... Akon ! It will be included on the singer's album re-release, scheduled for October 27. 

The song will be aired on radios in September. "Forgive Me", recently recorded (but available on the American version of her album Spirit), isn't included on the European version but it will be on the re-release, on October 27. The video will be directed by Wayne Usham & aired in September. 

Apart from "Forgive Me", the re-release of Spirit will include 2 other songs, "Misses Glass" & a cover of Snow Patrol's "Run". The album will have a new cover & a booklet. The Deluxe Hard Box edition will include a normal CD & a DVD including Leona Lewis' videos : "Bleeding Love" (European & American version), "Better In Time", "Footprints In The Sand", "Forgive Me"& "Run" & more images.
